OL,6,GThe BBC's director of nations says he
OL,7,Gdoesn't think the BBC is trying to take
OL,8,Gthe 'Local' out of Local Radio as
OL,9,Gproposed changes to the network of
OL,10,Gstations in England continue to face
OL,11,Gstrong criticism.
OL,13,FSpeaking to BBC Radio Derby's Ian Skye,
OL,14,FRhodri Talfan Davies admitted he had
OL,15,Freceived "hundreds and hundreds of
OL,16,Fletters" since the proposals were first
OL,17,Fannounced. He was criticised on-air for
OL,18,Ffailing to consult audiences and staff.
