OL,6,FThe BBC plans to cut back local radio
OL,7,Fprogrammes to run between 6am and 2pm
OL,8,Fon weekdays. During the remaining
OL,9,Fhours, local stations would carry a
OL,10,Frange of national, regional and
OL,11,Fsub-regional programmes, except when
OL,12,Flocal stations broadcast live sport.
OL,14,FThe BBC says the changes are needed in
OL,15,Forder to reallocate resources to online
OL,16,Fservices and local podcasts.
OL,18,FDavies admitted he'd received letters
OL,19,Fexpressing concern over plans for
OL,20,Fweekends and sharing programmes across
OL,21,Fcounty boundaries.
OL,3,CBBC boss claims broadcaster isn't
OL,4,Ctrying to take the 'Local' out of BBC
OL,5,CLocal Radio
