PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1668985137
OL,6,FHe told Ian Skye the BBC was listening
OL,7,Fto concerns from MPs, stakeholders,
OL,8,Flocal authorities and audiences,
OL,9,Femphasising the plans were still just
OL,10,Fproposals.
OL,12,FAn urgent question was raised in the
OL,13,FHouse of Commons last week when culture
OL,14,Fminister Julia Lopez confirmed the DCMS
OL,15,Fhadn't been briefed on the plans prior
OL,16,Fto publication. The minister confirmed
OL,17,Fshe would be meeting BBC bosses.
