OL,6,FMeanwhile, proposals to merge the BBC
OL,7,FNews Channel with its international
OL,8,Fcounterpart continue with less
OL,9,Fbacklash.
OL,11,FThe channel launched 25 years ago today
OL,12,Fas BBC News 24. Unlike 5 years ago, the
OL,13,Foccasion was not marked by the BBC on a
OL,14,Fday dominated by rolling news coverage
OL,15,Fof the US midterms simulcast with BBC
OL,16,FWorld News.
